Simple client and server vtTLS command-line applications

Installation:
- make clean;
- make

Define the following environment variables:
# sKnock definitions
export KNOCKPATH=/home/ubuntu/sKnock
export PYTHONPATH=/home/ubuntu/sKnock:$PYTHONPATH

Run server:
- ./server (runs on localhost on port 1111)

Run client:
- ./client <server-ip> <message-to-send>

